## Axiora v0.4.0 – MVP Foundation

### New Features
- User authentication
- Decision Board management
- Five readiness dimensions
- Evidence management (CRUD)
- File attachments
- Rule-based readiness analysis
- Dynamic recommendations
- Dynamic supporting and missing evidence

### Improvements
- Generic reusable Evidence Engine
- Dynamic scoring
- Improved analysis quality
- Navigation across all dimensions
- Supabase persistence

### Known Limitations
- Analysis is deterministic (rule-based), not AI-powered
- Multiple file upload not yet supported
- Analysis status does not yet update after analysis
- Import/Export functionality deferred
